<body>
    <div class="align">
        <div class="card" style="width: 30rem;height: 95vh;">
            <div class="bg-image hover-overlay ripple" data-mdb-ripple-color="light">
                <img src="image/loan.jpg" class="img-fluid" />
                <a href="#!">
                    <div class="mask" style="background-color: rgba(251, 251, 251, 0.15);"></div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Loan</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Different types of loans cater to specific needs and circumstances. Mortgages are
                    long-term loans used to finance property purchases, while auto loans are designed for purchasing
                    vehicles. Student loans support educational expenses, and business loans provide capital for
                    business operations or expansions. Personal loans can be used for a variety of purposes, from debt
                    consolidation to unexpected expenses.</p>
                <a href="./" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Home</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

